takowiki is a wiki software.


Designed to be useful for environment where engineers and non-engineers are working together and editing same document.

Engineers are people who want to edit the document in texteditor they like and manage the document by git. On the other hand, non-engineers want to edit some built-in WYSIWYG editor and have no ideas about any version management system.

To achive the goal, in takowiki
- Documents are managed in defualt file system of the os as a git repository.
- Each document are readable and editable in web browser like a wiki service.
